maize_chemical_benefits_other: -Maize germinated when the field is free from weeds and this made weeding easier.
-Weeds were controlled and this made weeding be done when not on preasure.
Chemicals burnt the weeds which gave her ample time to prepare for weeding and even doing other activities. ( There was reduced preasure for weeding)
-Reduced preasure during weeding since weeds were killed.
